      "role": "user",
      "content": "That sounds intense... and kind of scary. I don't know if I can trust something that sounds that sci-fi. If it's so \"miraculous,\" why hasn't everyone heard about it? Is there any way to just, i dont know, skip the whole process and just make the pain stop right now? Like, is there a permanent way to just be at peace without having to deal with all the therapy and stuff?",
